ersion":"blue","text":"The body is soft and rubbery. When angered, it will suck in air and inflate itself to an enormous size."},{"version":"yellow","text":"Its body is full of elasticity. By inhaling deeply, it can continue to inflate itself without limit."},{"version":"gold","text":"Their fur feels so good that if two of them snuggle together, they won't want to be separated."},{"version":"silver","text":"It has a very fine fur. Take care not to make it angry, or it may inflate steadily and hit with a BODY SLAM."},{"version":"crystal","text":"The rich, fluffy fur that covers its body feels so good that anyone who feels it can't stop touching it."},{"version":"ruby","text":"WIGGLYTUFF has large, saucerlike eyes. The surfaces of its eyes are always covered with a thin layer of tears. If any dust gets in this POK\u00e9MON\u2019s eyes, it is quickly washed away."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"WIGGLYTUFF\u2019s body is very flexible. By inhaling deeply, this POK\u00e9MON can inflate itself seemingly without end. Once inflated, WIGGLYTUFF bounces along lightly like a balloon."},{"version":"emerald","text":"Its fur is the ultimate in luxuriousness. Sleeping alongside a WIGGLYTUFF is simply divine. Its body expands seemingly without end when it inhales."},{"version":"firered","text":"Its fur is extremely fine, dense, and supple. The exquisitely pleasant fur conveys an image of luxury."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"The body is soft and rubbery. When angered, it will suck in air and inflate itself to an enormous size."},{"version":"diamond","text":"Its fine fur feels sublime to the touch. It can expand its body by inhaling air."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Its fine fur feels sublime to the touch. It can expand its body by inhaling air."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Its fine fur feels sublime to the touch. It can expand its body by inhaling air."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Their fur feels so good that if two of them snuggle together, they won\u2019t want to be separated."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It has a very fine fur. Take care not to make it angry, or it may inflate steadily and hit with a body slam."},{"version":"black","text":"Its fine fur feels sublime to the touch. It can expand its body by inhaling air."},{"version":"white","text":"Its fine fur feels sublime to the touch. It can expand its body by inhaling air."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Its fine fur feels so pleasant, those who accidentally touch it cannot take their hands away."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Its fine fur feels so pleasant, those who accidentally touch it cannot take their hands away."},{"version":"x","text":"Their fur feels so good that if two of them snuggle together, they won\u2019t want to be separated."},{"version":"y","text":"The body is soft and rubbery. When angered, it will suck in air and inflate itself to an enormous size."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Wigglytuff has large, saucerlike eyes. The surfaces of its eyes are always covered with a thin layer of tears. If any dust gets in this Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s eyes, it is quickly washed away."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Wigglytuff\u2019s body is very flexible. By inhaling deeply, this Pok\u00e9mon can inflate itself seemingly without end. Once inflated, Wigglytuff bounces along lightly like a balloon."},{"version":"sun","text":"It sheds its fine fur when the seasons change. The fur is gathered and spun into a luxurious yarn."},{"version":"moon","text":"As it inhales, it expands...and expands...and expands. Wigglytuff compete to see which one can inflate itself the most."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Thanks to its bouncy body and fine fur, this Pok\u00e9mon is sought after. Holding one in your arms while you sleep feels great."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"When it gets angry, it inhales with all its might, and its body gradually inflates. Sometimes they can grow 20 times larger!"},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Its body is very elastic. By inhaling deeply, it can continue to inflate itself without limit."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Its body is very elastic. By inhaling deeply, it can continue to inflate itself without limit."},{"version":"sword","text":"The more air it takes in, the more it inflates. If opponents catch it in a bad mood, it will inflate itself to an enormous size to intimidate them."},{"version":"shield","text":"It\u2019s proud of its fur, which is fine and delicate. In particular, the curl on its forehead has a texture that\u2019s perfectly heavenly."}],"evo":{"name":"igglybuff","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"jigglypuff","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":160,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"wigglytuff","level":2,"min_level":null,"trigger":"use-item","item":"moon-stone","held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/40.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/40.png","capture":50,"happiness":70,"growth":"fast","gender":6,"hatch":10,"ev":{"hp":3},"forms":[]}